{"tid":565184,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"西葡問題","createTime":"2018-02-18T17:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T11:24:42.000Z","uid":155601,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8474baf8ca25b1d60ee43eee0c9d0ea0c90a4a","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"準備五月尾去西葡, 想問下有無巴絲去過Toledo/Avila/Segovia/Aranjuez/Salamanca?評價如何?<br />\n另外葡萄牙Porto同Coimbra值唔得去<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旅遊台西葡資料好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761099198c89507efa2d46afda4e1cbf7ebe283a","tid":565184,"uid":22426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"如果鍾意紅酒嘅porto好值得去 好多酒窖慢慢行<br />\n唔飲酒嘅係海邊踩單車都好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7fb8aa4def56c5a043c643d4c0dcab075fa243","tid":565184,"uid":117917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T19:54:03.000Z","msg":"Toledo同Segovia都唔錯，toledo重點要係高處望先震撼，所以推薦搭佢個觀光巴士，10euro 24小時無限搭。Segovia 比toledo細，3個鐘內可行曬<br />\n。toledo 就半日左右。<br />\nAvila 將會去<br />\nSalamanca 將會去<br />\nAranjuez 麻麻地，時間多就去，無時間可省略，無咩野好睇。<br />\n<br />\nProto應該不錯，之後會去<br />\n<br />\n**係西班牙exchange緊"},{"pid":"7274024e42b02924e16ea8ddf518ea187b006912","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7fb8aa4def56c5a043c643d4c0dcab075fa243","tid":565184,"uid":117917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T19:54:03.000Z","msg":"Toledo同Segovia都唔錯，toledo重點要係高處望先震撼，所以推薦搭佢個觀光巴士，10euro 24小時無限搭。Segovia 比toledo細，3個鐘內可行曬<br />\n。toledo 就半日左右。<br />\nAvila 將會去<br />\nSalamanca 將會去<br />\nAranjuez 麻麻地，時間多就去，無時間可省略，無咩野好睇。<br />\n<br />\nProto應該不錯，之後會去<br />\n<br />\n**係西班牙exchange緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T21:18:22.000Z","msg":"去完分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e952e7924743b461675ddb5e05516a30f418ea14","tid":565184,"uid":92680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:28:22.000Z","msg":"segovia幾正 <br />\n座水壩幾值得影相 周邊仲有座城堡 好似可以入去參觀(不過我冇入)<br />\n<br />\n利伸 前排去完西葡"},{"pid":"8583ec05c268716b493670a4bbe93b29a7f4222d","tid":565184,"uid":53880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"Segovia座水道橋,教堂同城堡值得影相 , 城內可以行半日<br />\n城堡右面有條河 沿住行可以睇到靚既遠景 <br />\n乳豬就唔建議試 幾貴<br />\n如果想用成日係segovia 附近仲有座皇宮 搭巴士2-3euro單程 可以行半日<br />\n<br />\nToledo都係行半日<br />\n去城外影相打卡為主 有巴士 / 小火車都去到<br />\n城內有個主教堂 歷史同宗教意義好重 但入場都幾貴 <br />\n建築同其他大教堂差唔多 純睇景觀就唔建議入<br />\n沿住個城有條山道 鍾意行山散步可以hea行下<br />\n<br />\nSalamanca座大學幾靚 都值得去下<br />\n<br />\nAvila / Aranjuez冇去<br />\n<br />\n馬德里附近仲有cuenca 雖然冇去 聽人講都唔差<br />\n<br />\nPorto留1日半到2日<br />\n基本上1日內參觀哂 <br />\n主要留低食好野, 飲酒 享受下河畔風景 <br />\n留太耐又會悶"},{"pid":"b6590287efaa6c25316a9b98d11829b3ab2e0fa8","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T22:48:42.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a34bcc7ba5b16ba4254eddff886eabda7ed11f4","tid":565184,"uid":10448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T23:09:47.000Z","msg":"去過Cuenca 唔錯 啲建築物起係巨石上面都幾靚 不過地方唔係好大 預半日左右就夠<br />\n另外我自己覺得C&oacute;rdoba 嗰cathedral / mosque 都好特別 混合左Muslim 同 catholic <br />\n仲有Seville  嘅plaza de Espa&ntilde;a 好靚 ps. 如果你鐘意game of thrones 可以去埋 Real Alcazar (Dorne 取景嘅地方)"},{"pid":"5fc0c1c6549f7a31efe2a83eb5e897b1396d5670","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a34bcc7ba5b16ba4254eddff886eabda7ed11f4","tid":565184,"uid":10448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T23:09:47.000Z","msg":"去過Cuenca 唔錯 啲建築物起係巨石上面都幾靚 不過地方唔係好大 預半日左右就夠<br />\n另外我自己覺得C&oacute;rdoba 嗰cathedral / mosque 都好特別 混合左Muslim 同 catholic <br />\n仲有Seville  嘅plaza de Espa&ntilde;a 好靚 ps. 如果你鐘意game of thrones 可以去埋 Real Alcazar (Dorne 取景嘅地方)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:05:22.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSeville一定去"},{"pid":"05f5402047730b4840789cedfb11ec9061bcf9f7","tid":565184,"uid":157728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:42:35.000Z","msg":"記得去Granada 起碼2日1夜 睇個乜乜建築 要早好多book<br />\nCordoba 5月會有festival 睇下你中唔中"},{"pid":"2003f619409d0546398126d2b71f73a56152eee8","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f5402047730b4840789cedfb11ec9061bcf9f7","tid":565184,"uid":157728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:42:35.000Z","msg":"記得去Granada 起碼2日1夜 睇個乜乜建築 要早好多book<br />\nCordoba 5月會有festival 睇下你中唔中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打"},{"pid":"dfce3eec617c2c130a4075c7a99a5e881a37e658","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3981b19df0e000c31918f261efecf8d77a8b2f06","tid":565184,"uid":157728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2003f619409d0546398126d2b71f73a56152eee8","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f5402047730b4840789cedfb11ec9061bcf9f7","tid":565184,"uid":157728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:42:35.000Z","msg":"記得去Granada 起碼2日1夜 睇個乜乜建築 要早好多book<br />\nCordoba 5月會有festival 睇下你中唔中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"西葡都係果條route 嫁啦<br />\n成個trip最鍾意就係Barcelona 個灘 同 granada<br />\nMadrid 悶到迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a47bcb96da86162f4924b39470623d13e4c08e7","tid":565184,"uid":112076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"留多啲時間去細城市啦 <br />\nGranada 我去左 暑假去好多人 去之前記得要boo