hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"西班牙除左馬德里大城貴d 之外，其他城消費都係合理仲平過香港。而且超市街市又多，食野買野都平。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/170642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F170642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ad56f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁大碟飯好食之余夠4個人食都係十幾歐<br />\n<br />\n另外名牌好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己一喼去三喼番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/170848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F170848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=50e6591e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記住買火腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9245886f343365f2e20d976077c65ba3987721d","tid":565184,"uid":157728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"呀屌仲有<br />\nMadrid有間野話係健力士最早開既餐廳 <br />\n間野係大廣場附近 好近<br />\n晚餐要book 午餐睇彩數<br />\n食過佢既乳豬 正到仆街 <br />\n我果時係食lunch 再去Segovia來回 咁樣玩一日"},{"pid":"83cfa0a3840b9a7bb58d50fdfb6ad14c57e4889d","tid":565184,"uid":2545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa57eb18e0c072276846588a5e6606d633915f1c","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf46bfac41757e0d3ce1d65e561e584598c9cadf","tid":565184,"uid":2545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T23:58:55.000Z","msg":"我前年去Porto &amp; Lisbon加埋4日定5日<br />\nLisbon好正，好多野食又平<br />\n葡撻真係世界級（講緊果間百年老店）<br />\n想今年再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji