":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5a530c3d17632c3c462d1ebe010ef3b557ec86d","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"葡國菜有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西班牙野會唔會好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"西班牙除左馬德里大城貴d 之外，其他城消費都係合理仲平過香港。而且超市街市又多，食野買野都平。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/170642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F170642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ad56f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁大碟飯好食之余夠4個人食都係十幾歐<br />\n<br />\n另外名牌好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己一喼去三喼番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/170848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F170848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=50e6591e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記住買火腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"除左Zara有咩名牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"Loewe 包包 Camper 鞋 Carmina 皮鞋<br />\n另外仲有Channel BV Rimova 呢d 大路牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b2dc949b95b5d755c525d0775dc1244f770bc2","tid":565184,"uid":120654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80a192b9035fdd325a8abeac0b0b798c49265e80","tid":565184,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9245886f343365f2e20d976077c65ba3987721d","tid":565184,"uid":157728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"呀屌仲有<br />\nMadrid有間野話係健力士最早開既餐廳 <br />\n間野係大廣場附近 好近<br />\n晚餐要book 午餐睇彩數<br />\n食過佢既乳豬 正到仆街 <br />\n我果時係食lunch 再去Segovia來回 咁樣玩一日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:19:50.000Z","msg":"去試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:49:16.000Z","msg":"可以上網book. 個乳豬同sangria 都好正"},{"pid":"221db42df0b5e37c93c98fc266fa033635aeb858","tid":565184,"uid":51744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d8495cc085d7aa0ff0cca6c0834c4c31d9a608f","tid":565184,"uid":106326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:24:24.000Z","msg":"睇返你地啲相好想再去過<br />\n曾經係葡萄牙生活過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPorto 值得去 但又唔洗話花好多日<br />\n畢竟啲野都幾集中<br />\n但我會建議你花一個下午去坐沿海線既捷運<br />\n有一段路係路軌都係草地黎<br />\n附近有個海灘<br />\n個頭曾經係一個港口黎，有啲古船停泊係度。<br />\n我已經搵唔返了。<br />\n但波圖既捷運線沿景真係值得花時間去欣賞。覺得邊度靚就可以落車去睇睇<br />\n<br />\n里斯本我想介紹一個鄰近既小鎮<br />\n叫Cascais<br />\n里斯本有火車去到<br />\n我個陣係住係一個退休大叔既屋企。<br />\n個度係過去皇族黎渡假勝地黎<br />\n我會建議你係estoril 個一帶落車然後慢慢散步過去<br />\n個邊既商店街係我見過最有童話色彩最夢幻。<br />\n<br />\n我仲去過Santarem, 做牧場工，然後去左中部好多既小鎮，真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我又係搵唔返個名，但其中一個鎮係有個鬥技場，有個係山丘上既小教堂，望住條河同日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超靚<br />\n<br />\n相比之下coimbra其實幾個鐘就行得晒<br />\n主要都係晒商店街同大學，仲有河畔區<br />\n有時間可以去，無亦唔太可惜<br />\n<br />\n去Porto之前我仲去左Aveiro<br />\n因為人地介紹係葡萄牙既威尼斯<br />\n咁去到當然知道唔係個回事啦<br />\n但都係一個幾靚既小鎮<br />\n我住左三日當地人既屋企<br />\n介紹左好多朋友比我識<br />\n仲帶我去佢大學參觀，去睇當地一間百年甜點店既工場參觀試食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙係我去旅行停留得最耐既其中一個國家<br />\n即使係一個月都睇唔晒<br />\n仲有好多好多地方想去再去過<br />\n<br />\n但返黎之後比人笑 個個玩葡萄牙最多都係幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"足足一個月... 10日LISBON，10日PORTO，10日MADEIRA"}]}